<div><head>楚竹書六《魯邦大旱》</head>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4534_CHANT_001-1a.1"><pb xml:id="CH8x4534_CHANT_001-1a" ed="CHANT" n="001-1a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4534_CHANT_001-1a.2">魯邦大旱，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4534_CHANT_001-1a.3">哀公謂孔子：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4534_CHANT_001-1a.4">「子不為我圖之？」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4534_CHANT_001-1a.5">孔子對曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4534_CHANT_001-1a.6">「邦大旱，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4534_CHANT_001-1a.7">毋乃失諸刑與德乎？<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4534_CHANT_001-1a.8">唯正刑與德。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4534_CHANT_001-1a.9">哀公曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4534_CHANT_001-1a.10">「庶民以我不知以說之事鬼也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4534_CHANT_001-1a.11">若<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4534_CHANT_001-1a.12">之何哉？」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4534_CHANT_001-1a.13">孔子曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4534_CHANT_001-1a.14">「庶民知說之事，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4534_CHANT_001-1a.15">鬼也，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4534_CHANT_001-1a.16">不知刑與德。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4534_CHANT_001-1a.17">汝毋愛珪璧幣帛於山川，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4534_CHANT_001-1a.18">正刑與德，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4534_CHANT_001-1a.19">以事上天，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4534_CHANT_001-1a.20">鬼神感之，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4534_CHANT_001-1a.21">大旱必止矣。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4534_CHANT_001-1a.22">公曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4534_CHANT_001-1a.23">「善哉。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4534_CHANT_001-1a.24">孔子出，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4534_CHANT_001-1a.25">遇子貢曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4534_CHANT_001-1a.26">「賜爾聞巷路之言，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4534_CHANT_001-1a.27">毋乃謂丘之對非歟？」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4534_CHANT_001-1a.28">子貢曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4534_CHANT_001-1a.29">「否，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4534_CHANT_001-1a.30">抑吾子乃重命其歟？<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4534_CHANT_001-1a.31">若夫正刑與德，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4534_CHANT_001-1a.32">以事上天，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4534_CHANT_001-1a.33">此是哉。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4534_CHANT_001-1a.34">若夫毋愛珪璧<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4534_CHANT_001-1a.35">幣帛於山川，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4534_CHANT_001-1a.36">毋乃不可。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4534_CHANT_001-1a.37">「夫山，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4534_CHANT_001-1a.38">石以為膚，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4534_CHANT_001-1a.39">木以為民，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4534_CHANT_001-1a.40">如天不雨，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4534_CHANT_001-1a.41">石將焦，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4534_CHANT_001-1a.42">木將死，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4534_CHANT_001-1a.43">其欲雨有甚於我，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4534_CHANT_001-1a.44">又必待乎命乎？<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4534_CHANT_001-1a.45">夫川，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4534_CHANT_001-1a.46">水以為膚，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4534_CHANT_001-1a.47">魚以為民，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4534_CHANT_001-1a.48">如天不雨，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4534_CHANT_001-1a.49">水將涸，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4534_CHANT_001-1a.50">魚將死，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4534_CHANT_001-1a.51">其欲雨有甚於我，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4534_CHANT_001-1a.52">何必祠乎命乎？」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4534_CHANT_001-1a.53">孔子曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4534_CHANT_001-1a.54">「鳴呼！<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4534_CHANT_001-1a.55">賜也，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4534_CHANT_001-1a.56">我告爾：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4534_CHANT_001-1a.57">命也者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4534_CHANT_001-1a.58">君子以為文，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4534_CHANT_001-1a.59">庶民以為神。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4534_CHANT_001-1a.60">如不命，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4534_CHANT_001-1a.61">王<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4534_CHANT_001-1a.62">公豈不養任糧肉哉，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4534_CHANT_001-1a.63">抑無如庶民何？」<lb/></seg>
</p>
